<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="announcement-n">announcement <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'naʊnsmənt/    美 /ə'naʊnsmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] 通告；布告 [U] 宣布；宣告：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make an announcement</strong>
宣布通告</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I read the <strong>announcement of</strong> the summer camp that you have posted on the Internet and I am interested in it.
阅读了你们在网上发布的夏令营布告，对此我很感兴趣。</p><footer>2012 全国书面表达</footer></div></div>